00:08:03.366 --> 00:08:05.476 A:middle
Before we begin, imagine I'm a

00:08:05.476 --> 00:08:07.236 A:middle
developer and these are all of

00:08:07.236 --> 00:08:08.526 A:middle
the assets that I've uploaded to

00:08:08.656 --> 00:08:10.466 A:middle
App Store Connect for my app,

00:08:10.986 --> 00:08:11.526 A:middle
