00:08:43.436 --> 00:08:44.726 A:middle
I can use Creative Sets to

00:08:44.726 --> 00:08:46.106 A:middle
choose the assets that best

00:08:46.136 --> 00:08:47.466 A:middle
align to those themes.

00:08:48.476 --> 00:08:49.596 A:middle
Let's go through the steps of

00:08:49.596 --> 00:08:51.306 A:middle
